===Noun===
{{en-noun|es}}

# {{lb|en|meteorology|astronomy}} A very [[rare]] [[phenomenon]] observed in the [[morning]] or [[evening]] when the [[sun]] is crossing or immediately below the [[horizon]], in which a [[momentary]] flash of blue light appears above the upper [[rim]] of the solar disk, caused by [[refraction]] of light in the [[atmosphere]].
# {{lb|en|nuclear physics}} A phenomenon sometimes observed when a [[criticality]] [[incident]] occurs in [[nuclear]] materials, inducing a discharge of [[radiation]] into the environment.

